        obtain ⟨p, hp1, hp2⟩ := h2.2
        obtain ⟨p', hp1', hp2'⟩ := h3.2
        obtain ⟨p'', hp1'', hp2''⟩ := h4.2
        obtain ⟨p''', hp1''', hp2'''⟩ := h5.2
        obtain ⟨p'''', hp1'''', hp2''''⟩ := h6.2

                norm_cast at * <;>
              ring_nf at * <;>
            norm_cast at * <;>
          omega

}
